\begin_layout Plain Layout
Binomial pgf: 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{k}\left[\frac{\Gamma(n+1)}{\Gamma(k+1)\Gamma(n-k+1)}\cdot p^{k}(1-p)^{n-k}\smiley^{k}\right]=\sum_{k}\left[\frac{\Gamma(n+1)}{\Gamma(k+1)\Gamma(n-k+1)}\cdot\left[p\smiley\right]^{k}(1-p)^{n-k}\right]=[(1-p)+p\smiley]^{n}$
\end_inset


