Because Binomial Theorem is that 
\begin_inset Formula $(x+y)^{n}=\sum_{k}^{\infty}\left[\binom{n}{k}x^{k}y^{n-k}\right]$
\end_inset

.
 Note that this works for even non-integer values of n.
